  "name": "nged-projects-connections-reforms-outcomes",
  "notes": "The NGED Projects Connections Reforms Outcomes contains details of all projects submitted by National Grid Electricity Distribution (NGED) as part of the CMP435 process. The outcome dataset includes only those projects managed directly by NGED and therefore excludes larger projects overseen by the National Energy System Operator (NESO). The dataset provides an inventory of projects outcomes, assessments and protections as a result from the reform process.  \r\n\r\nFor CMP435 outcomes and queue positions please visit Clearview pages: [National Grid - Clearview](https://connections.nationalgrid.co.uk/clear-view/)\r\n",
